Raped the women and
killed their children.

650
01:00:50,167 --> 01:00:54,582
It was the Indian army that
shed blood to save Kashmir.

651
01:00:56,433 --> 01:00:59,710
- And if we aren't around,
it'll happen again.

652
01:00:59,900 --> 01:01:03,347
Does the law allow you to torture
people you've arrested?

653
01:01:03,400 --> 01:01:05,641
The Indian army is one of the most...

654
01:01:05,700 --> 01:01:08,078
disciplined armed
forces in the world.

655
01:01:08,500 --> 01:01:12,448
We train our officers to interrogate,
and not torture.

656
01:01:12,567 --> 01:01:17,846
Amidst militant attacks,
today Kashmir goes to vote.

657
01:01:17,900 --> 01:01:20,972
Militant groups have
exploded bombs in...

658
01:01:21,034 --> 01:01:23,776
Srinagar, Barahmulla and Anantnag.

659
01:01:24,667 --> 01:01:26,977
I want you to understand
the ground reality.

660
01:01:27,034 --> 01:01:30,538
Separatists are not demanding
freedom from India...

661
01:01:32,634 --> 01:01:34,580
but enslavement to Pakistan.

662
01:01:34,633 --> 01:01:38,809
- Indian troops coerced reluctant
voters into polling booths.

663
