- India has rubbished these allegations.

664
01:01:41,434 --> 01:01:44,381
- However, the voter turnout
remained very low.

665
01:01:44,433 --> 01:01:47,004
- Koshmar constituency saw
the lowest turn out...

666
01:01:47,067 --> 01:01:49,513
where only 110 votes were registered.

667
01:01:49,667 --> 01:01:50,737
- Congratulations!

668
01:01:50,800 --> 01:01:51,904
You have won by a hundred votes.

669
01:01:51,967 --> 01:01:54,106
Congratulations!
- Congratulations!

670
01:02:10,600 --> 01:02:13,638
These traditional folk entertainers
known as Bhand...

671
01:02:13,700 --> 01:02:16,909
are enacting a play
which speaks of a new Kashmir...

672
01:02:17,533 --> 01:02:18,739
- A peaceful Kashmir...

673
01:02:18,800 --> 01:02:22,270
- will the new regime bring
a brighter future for Kashmir?

674
01:02:22,667 --> 01:02:24,271
Only time will tell.

675
01:03:56,834 --> 01:03:57,812
Nice...

676
01:04:02,200 --> 01:04:03,611
Very nice article.

677
01:04:06,434 --> 01:04:07,378
Thank you.

678
01:04:09,667 --> 01:04:12,273
- Come inside...

679
01:04:13,500 --> 01:04:14,911
Come in...

680
01:04:15,167 --> 01:04:16,612
Why are you standing there?

681
01:04:16,667 --> 01:04:18,510
