783
01:13:21,134 --> 01:13:22,579
- Long live India!
- Long live India!

784
01:13:22,600 --> 01:13:25,376
Long live India!

785
01:13:30,501 --> 01:13:33,607
Since that day doctor
and I were always together...

786
01:13:33,667 --> 01:13:36,307
like body and soul...

787
01:13:37,467 --> 01:13:41,472
We bore our torments together
in the same cell.

788
01:13:42,167 --> 01:13:44,272
We were chained together.

789
01:13:46,334 --> 01:13:49,679
It seems we will be
killed together as well.

790
01:13:51,067 --> 01:13:54,139
You can die doctor, but I won't.

791
01:13:56,534 --> 01:13:57,945
And how is that?

792
01:13:58,501 --> 01:14:01,414
You are the body
and I'm the soul...

793
01:14:01,467 --> 01:14:04,073
You are mortal and I'm immortal!

794
01:14:07,467 --> 01:14:10,346
Are you a Shia or a Sunni?

795
01:14:12,000 --> 01:14:14,913
I am the river and the tree...

796
01:14:15,434 --> 01:14:18,244
The Jhelum and the Chinar...

797
01:14:19,601 --> 01:14:22,411
I'm both..
a temple and a mosque...

798
01:14:23,134 --> 01:14:25,637
A Shia and a Sunni, I'm both.

799
01:14:27,167 --> 01:14:28,942
A Hindu as well.

800
01:14:30,634 --> 01:14:33,376
I always was... I am...

801
01:14:34,334 --> 01:14:36,280
I will always be...

802
