camps for interrogation.

803
01:14:44,467 --> 01:14:47,573
Strange camps... stranger names...

804
01:14:49,867 --> 01:14:52,871
Bo-Bo land, Hotel 6...

805
01:14:53,034 --> 01:14:54,274
Faraz cinema...

806
01:15:37,434 --> 01:15:42,315
And one day, there was a revelation.

807
01:15:45,534 --> 01:15:48,276
It was Khurram who
betrayed your father.

808
